{"tid":1345040,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"元朗警：做大事願付出畢生代價 被誤會亦絕未會作罷","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:31:36.000Z","uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7be9e6ceaabf1097f6bdc07f4ab191dba4f1d869","tid":1345040,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Axhlv3CPI_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAxhlv3CPI_w&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=c8b8e3c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Axhlv3CPI_w</a><br />\n<br />\nThats Right<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《一字馬》<br />\n<br />\n作曲：黃尚偉 <br />\n作詞：周禮茂<br />\n主唱：林保怡<br />\n<br />\n做大事願付出畢生代價<br />\n被誤會亦絕未會作罷<br />\n大命運未在手中不驚怕<br />\n沒一點小刺激　剩下日子都枉去花<br />\n<br />\n任世界再變化　明日來了我笑一下<br />\n但世界買我怕　不相信空口說白話<br />\n做大事　做就盡力做<br />\n像一匹飛天馬（Let's Fly）<br />\n自己都敢叫好　叫敵對不敢說話<br />\n直到天空宇宙　給我盡騎下<br />\n（LA LA LA LA LA LA LA LA）<br />\n做到不枉以後　一切化灰　只需一紮花<br />\n<br />\n男人心一字馬　讓女人心擔驚受怕<br />\n未必不會念掛　淚眼說知己說話<br />\n男人不一字馬　讓女人艷麗也黯啞<br />\n若鮮花也謝了　任再歸我亦無家<br />\n<br />\n大命運未在手中不驚怕<br />\n沒一點小刺激　剩下日子都枉去花"},{"pid":"10159344b7488c1c5b26f8d9c32587da0b855616","tid":1345040,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:15:37.000Z","msg":"自己都敢叫好　叫敵對不敢說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10b9786b3c51cfecbef832240b05f9dfc7b01dc","tid":1345040,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpRX28T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpRX28T.jpg&h=f180a06c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7700c6f85ad65ccb77913e020eb98014d0a83e0e","tid":1345040,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 